---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Button from '../../components/Button.astro';
import QuoteBlock from '../../components/QuoteBlock.astro';
import SectionDivider from '../../components/SectionDivider.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Magnalia" description="The journal of Catholic cultural renewal in Canada. Essays, art, and letters from leading Catholic thinkers.">

  <!-- Section 1: Hero -->
  <section class="section section--dark magnalia-hero">
    <div class="container magnalia-hero__inner">
      <div class="magnalia-hero__text">
        <p class="label text-gold">The Journal of Catholic Cultural Renewal in Canada</p>
        <h1 class="magnalia-hero__title display">Magnalia</h1>
        <p class="magnalia-hero__subtitle"><em>Great and wonderful things</em></p>
        <p class="magnalia-hero__body">
          Magnalia brings together the finest Catholic writing, scholarship, and art in Canada. Each
          60-page issue features original essays from leading Catholic thinkers, letters from the field,
          and beautiful visual art. Published twice yearly by the Gregory the Great Institute.
        </p>
        <div class="magnalia-hero__ctas">
          <Button href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}magnalia/subscribe/`} variant="secondary">Subscribe to Magnalia</Button>
          <a href="#sample" class="magnalia-hero__link">Read a Sample →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="magnalia-hero__cover">
        <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/branding/Magnalia_Cover.jpg`} alt="Magnalia Journal — Issue One" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 2: Inside Issue One — Highlight Strip -->
  <section class="section section--tight">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <p class="label text-gold">Inside Issue One · Winter 2026 · 60 Pages</p>
        <h2>What You'll Find</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="highlights-strip reveal">
        <div class="highlight-card">
          <span class="highlight-card__type label text-gold">Essay</span>
          <h3 class="highlight-card__title">Heart Speaks to Heart</h3>
          <p class="highlight-card__author">Thomas Cardinal Collins</p>
          <p class="highlight-card__desc">The Archbishop Emeritus of Toronto on Newman's motto and the renewal of Catholic culture in Canada.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-card">
          <span class="highlight-card__type label text-gold">Essay</span>
          <h3 class="highlight-card__title">Irrigating the New Deserts</h3>
          <p class="highlight-card__author">Dr. Ryan N.S. Topping</p>
          <p class="highlight-card__desc">The case for Catholic institution-building in an age of cultural drought — and a roadmap for how to begin.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-card">
          <span class="highlight-card__type label text-gold">Essay</span>
          <h3 class="highlight-card__title">The Nursery Rhyme Metaphysic</h3>
          <p class="highlight-card__author">Dr. Celene Sidloski</p>
          <p class="highlight-card__desc">How the imaginative world of childhood verse encodes deep truths about reality.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-card">
          <span class="highlight-card__type label text-gold">Essay</span>
          <h3 class="highlight-card__title">AI and the Future of Humanity</h3>
          <p class="highlight-card__author">Dr. Gerard McLarney</p>
          <p class="highlight-card__desc">A Catholic philosopher confronts the promises and perils of artificial intelligence.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="highlights-more">Plus essays, reviews, art, and more. <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}magnalia/issue-one/`}>See full table of contents →</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <SectionDivider />

  <!-- Section 3: Sample Content -->
  <section class="section" id="sample">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="sample-article reveal">
        <p class="label text-gold">Sample from Issue One</p>
        <h2 class="sample-article__title">Irrigating the New Deserts</h2>
        <p class="sample-article__byline">By <strong>Dr. Ryan N.S. Topping</strong></p>

        <div class="prose">
          <p>
            Catholic culture in Canada is not dying. It is being born again — but only where men and
            women have the courage to build. The great institutions that once carried the faith through
            centuries — the universities, the hospitals, the schools — were not handed down from heaven.
            They were built, stone by stone, by people who understood that culture is the fruit of worship.
          </p>
          <p>
            We face a new kind of desert. Not the desert of persecution, but the desert of indifference —
            a landscape in which the faith is not opposed but simply forgotten. In this desert, the old
            institutions have dried up or lost their nerve. The question is not whether Catholic culture
            can survive, but whether we have the will to irrigate new ground.
          </p>
          <blockquote class="sample-article__pullquote">
            <p>"The task before us is not to restore what was, but to build what must be — institutions worthy of the tradition we have received."</p>
          </blockquote>
          <p>
            What does this mean in practice? It means new journals, new schools, new centres of formation.
            It means taking seriously the intellectual life — not as a luxury for academics, but as a
            necessity for every baptized person. It means refusing to accept that Catholic culture in
            Canada is a relic of the past rather than a seed of the future...
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="sample-article__cta">
          <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/branding/Magnalia_Cover.jpg`} alt="Magnalia Issue One" class="sample-article__cta-cover" />
          <div class="sample-article__cta-content">
            <p class="sample-article__cta-text">Subscribe to read the full issue and future editions.</p>
            <Button href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}magnalia/subscribe/`} variant="primary">Subscribe to Magnalia</Button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 4: Contributors -->
  <section class="section section--linen">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <p class="label text-gold">Who Writes Magnalia</p>
        <h2>Our Contributors</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="contributors-grid reveal">
        <div class="contributor-card">
          <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/people/Ryan-Topping-headshot.jpg`} alt="Dr. Ryan Topping" class="contributor-card__photo" />
          <h3 class="contributor-card__name">Dr. Ryan N.S. Topping</h3>
          <p class="contributor-card__credentials">DPhil (Oxford) · 11 books</p>
          <p class="contributor-card__bio">Executive Director. Catholic education and cultural philosophy.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="contributor-card">
          <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/people/Celene-Sidloski-headshot.jpg`} alt="Dr. Celene Sidloski" class="contributor-card__photo" />
          <h3 class="contributor-card__name">Dr. Celene Sidloski</h3>
          <p class="contributor-card__credentials">Fellow · Saskatoon</p>
          <p class="contributor-card__bio">Classical education and Canadian Catholic intellectual life.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="contributor-card">
          <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/people/Joe-Woodard-headshot.jpg`} alt="Dr. Joseph Woodard" class="contributor-card__photo" />
          <h3 class="contributor-card__name">Dr. Joseph Woodard</h3>
          <p class="contributor-card__credentials">Fellow · Calgary</p>
          <p class="contributor-card__bio">Ethics, bioethics, and Catholic social thought.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="contributor-card">
          <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/people/Mark-Ingham-headshot.jpg`} alt="Mark Ingham" class="contributor-card__photo" />
          <h3 class="contributor-card__name">Mark Ingham</h3>
          <p class="contributor-card__credentials">Fellow · Barry's Bay · PhD Cand.</p>
          <p class="contributor-card__bio">Vocations research and Canadian Catholic demographics.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="section-footer">
        <Button href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}magnalia/contributors/`} variant="tertiary">Meet All Contributors →</Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <SectionDivider />

  <!-- Section 5: Subscription Options Preview -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Read Magnalia</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="sub-tiers reveal">
        <div class="sub-tier">
          <h3 class="sub-tier__name">Single Copy</h3>
          <p class="sub-tier__price">$45</p>
          <p class="sub-tier__desc">Try a single issue of Magnalia.</p>
          <Button href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}magnalia/subscribe/`} variant="secondary" size="small">Order a Copy</Button>
        </div>
        <div class="sub-tier sub-tier--featured">
          <p class="sub-tier__badge label">Most Popular</p>
          <h3 class="sub-tier__name">Annual Subscription</h3>
          <p class="sub-tier__price">$80<span class="sub-tier__period">/year</span></p>
          <p class="sub-tier__desc">Two issues per year. The standard for Friends of Magnalia.</p>
          <Button href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}magnalia/subscribe/`} variant="primary" size="small">Subscribe</Button>
        </div>
        <div class="sub-tier">
          <h3 class="sub-tier__name">Magnalia Patron</h3>
          <p class="sub-tier__price">$600<span class="sub-tier__period">/year</span></p>
          <p class="sub-tier__desc">Subscription + named recognition + quarterly Q&A with the editor.</p>
          <Button href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}magnalia/subscribe/`} variant="secondary" size="small">Become a Patron</Button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="sub-student-note">Students & seminarians: 50% off any subscription · <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}magnalia/subscribe/`}>View all options →</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 6: Magnalia Letter Cross-sell -->
  <section class="section section--dark">
    <div class="container" style="text-align: center; max-width: 600px;">
      <h2 style="color: var(--color-text-on-dark); margin-bottom: 12px;">Between Issues</h2>
      <p style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 1rem; color: rgba(245,239,229,0.8); margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.7;">
        Stay connected with the Magnalia Letter — a free monthly essay from the Institute, plus event invitations
        and reading recommendations.
      </p>
      <form class="newsletter-section__form" action="#" method="POST" style="justify-content: center;">
        <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Email address" class="newsletter-inline-input" required aria-label="Email address" />
        <button type="submit" class="newsletter-inline-btn">Subscribe Free</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Hero */
  .magnalia-hero__inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-component);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .magnalia-hero__title {
    color: var(--color-text-on-dark);
    margin: 8px 0 4px;
  }

  .magnalia-hero__subtitle {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: rgba(245, 239, 229, 0.75);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .magnalia-hero__body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(245, 239, 229, 0.8);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .magnalia-hero__ctas {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 20px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .magnalia-hero__link {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: rgba(245, 239, 229, 0.6);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .magnalia-hero__link:hover {
    color: var(--color-gold);
  }

  .magnalia-hero__cover img {
    max-width: 360px;
    width: 100%;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: block;
    transform: rotate(-2deg);
    box-shadow: 0 16px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
    border-radius: 3px;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .magnalia-hero__inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
    }
  }

  /* Highlight Strip */
  .section--tight {
    padding-block: 40px;
  }

  .highlights-strip {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .highlight-card {
    background-color: var(--color-linen);
    border: 1px solid rgba(90, 90, 110, 0.08);
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 20px 24px;
  }

  .highlight-card__type {
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .highlight-card__title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-navy);
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .highlight-card__author {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-gray);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .highlight-card__desc {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--color-gray);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .highlights-more {
    text-align: center;
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--color-gray);
    margin-top: 20px;
  }

  .highlights-more a {
    color: var(--color-gold);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .highlights-more a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .highlights-strip {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .highlights-strip {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    }
  }

  /* Sample Article */
  .sample-article {
    max-width: var(--max-prose-width);
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  .sample-article__title {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin: 8px 0 12px;
  }

  .sample-article__byline {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-gray);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    padding-bottom: 24px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(90, 90, 110, 0.1);
  }

  .sample-article__pullquote {
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-gold);
    padding-left: 24px;
    margin: 32px 0;
  }

  .sample-article__pullquote p {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-navy);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .sample-article__cta {
    margin-top: 40px;
    padding-top: 32px;
    border-top: 2px solid var(--color-gold);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .sample-article__cta-cover {
    width: 120px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    border-radius: 3px;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    transform: rotate(-2deg);
  }

  .sample-article__cta-content {
    text-align: left;
  }

  .sample-article__cta-text {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-gray);
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .sample-article__cta {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .sample-article__cta-cover {
      width: 100px;
    }
    .sample-article__cta-content {
      text-align: center;
    }
  }

  /* Contributors */
  .contributors-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .contributor-card {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 24px 16px;
  }

  .contributor-card__photo {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center top;
    display: block;
    margin: 0 auto 12px;
  }

  .contributor-card__name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-navy);
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .contributor-card__credentials {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .contributor-card__bio {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-gray);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .contributors-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    }
  }

  /* Subscription Tiers */
  .sub-tiers {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  .sub-tier {
    background-color: var(--color-linen);
    border: 1px solid rgba(90, 90, 110, 0.1);
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 28px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .sub-tier--featured {
    border: 2px solid var(--color-gold);
  }

  .sub-tier__badge {
    color: var(--color-gold);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .sub-tier__name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-navy);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .sub-tier__price {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-navy);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .sub-tier__period {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--color-gray);
  }

  .sub-tier__desc {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-gray);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .sub-tiers {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .sub-student-note {
    text-align: center;
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--color-gray);
    margin-top: 16px;
  }

  .sub-student-note a {
    color: var(--color-gold);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .sub-student-note a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  /* Inline newsletter in dark section */
  .newsletter-inline-input {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    background: rgba(245, 239, 229, 0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(245, 239, 229, 0.2);
    border-radius: 3px;
    color: var(--color-text-on-dark);
    outline: none;
    min-width: 240px;
    transition: border-color var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .newsletter-inline-input:focus {
    border-color: var(--color-gold);
  }

  .newsletter-inline-input::placeholder {
    color: rgba(245, 239, 229, 0.35);
  }

  .newsletter-inline-btn {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 12px 24px;
    background-color: var(--color-gold);
    color: var(--color-navy);
    border: none;
    border-radius: 3px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background-color var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .newsletter-inline-btn:hover {
    background-color: #a08638;
  }

  /* Shared */
  .section--linen {
    background-color: var(--color-linen);
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-component);
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  .section-footer {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: var(--space-component);
  }
</style>
